## [0.2.1] - 2016-06-17

### Changed
- Usage examples in README.md

### Added
- This change log

## [0.2.0] - 2016-06-17

### Changed
- All independent functionality moved from ConsoleCommand to traits
- Terminal detection moved to separate TerminalInfo class

### Added
- Composer package
- Usage examples
- Widget that allows to select one answer from predefined answers list
- Widget for console header
- Widget for console tables
- Manipulation with reach console output through ConsoleCommand->disableReachOutput() and ConsoleCommand->enableReachOutput() methods

### Deprecated
- Enabling and disabling of reach console output, switching ConsoleCommand->useColors flag
- Usage of RCli::writeString()

### Fixed
- Switching reach output status bug

### Removed
- References to Yii console component

## [0.1.0] - 2015-04-03

### Added
- ConsoleCommand as a base class for all console applications
- Reach text formatting for console messages

## [0.0.0] - 2013-07-02
### Added
- Initial commit with basic functionality